comments: Hampton (ORL) dislodges Mathurin (IND) from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Bamba (ORL) is firming up in Nesmith's (IND) path when marginal contact occurs during the off-ball screen.
Bamba (ORL) brings his hands toward Nesmith (IND) and marginal contact occurs as Bamba releases away to roll.
Turner (IND) contests Wagner's (ORL) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs as Wagner returns to the floor.
Nesmith (IND) and Wagner (ORL) mutually engage and disengage off-ball.
Mathurin (IND) is trailing Suggs (ORL) and retracts his hands when marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Bamba (ORL) firms up over his left foot in Mathurin's (IND) path when marginal contact occurs while setting the pick.
Mathurin (IND) takes a step toward Suggs (ORL) when marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Suggs (ORL) moves into Halbiurton's (IND) lower body, dislodging him from his position during the loose ball.
Hield (IND) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Bol (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball to briefly dislodge it prior to incidental contact occurring with Nesmith (IND).
Bamba (ORL) reaches in and initiates contact with Nesmith's (IND) arm and lower body, affecting his ability to maintain possession of the ball.
Nesmith (IND) jumps alongside Wagner's (ORL) path to legally contest the driving shot attempt.
McConnell (IND) places his forearm on Bamba's (ORL) body and marginal contact occurs as Bamba moves toward the rebound.
Nembhard (IND) is jumping toward the rebound when marginal contact occurs with Bamba (ORL) on the put-back shot attempt.
